Package jetbrains.mps.openapi.editor.menus

Interface EditorMenuTrace

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EditorMenuTrace.EmptyEditorMenuTrace, EditorMenuTraceImpl
    public interface EditorMenuTrace
    The interface representing the editor menu trace in the process of building the transformation/substitute menu. Available from TransformationMenuContext and SubstituteMenuContext One may push the trace info on the stack, pop the trace info from the stack, get the current trace info from the top of the stack and set the menu descriptor to the current trace info
    See Also:
    EditorMenuTraceInfo
